trailingComments.value:
*
 * Execute a sequence of operations.
 * Wraps `language-common/execute`, and prepends initial state for http.
 * @function execute
 * @memberof Adaptor
 * @example 
 * execute(
 *   create('foo'),
 *   delete('bar')
 * )(state)
 * @constructor
 * @param {Operations} operations - Operations to be performed.
 * @returns {Operation}
